review: Dr was very helpful and explained the problem very well and she makes pateint comfortable.  She doesnt give u full bags of medicine but gives only which needed. Worth visiting dr prabhjot
This was my first time. She listened to my issues without any fuss.  She was friendly and understood the problem clearly.

Doctor was unavailable for more than 45 minutes from appointment time. The Staff was not clear and misguided on wait time. We could not meet the doctor at all.

My mother 73 years old could not wait for an seemingly long time due to COVID related risks prevailing in our area.

I would recommend the staff and the doctor maintain some transparency and proactive communication with patients who are waiting for consultation.

If the staff could have informed us yesterday via a phone call to come later as doctor was unavailable it would have saved us a lot of inconvenience.

Thanks
She is nice and have patience to listen . She recommended me medicine and now I am feeling better . Thank you

review: i had visited this doctor with the problem of pain in the left breast and surrounding areashe did asked me about my periods and when i said it's one day gone than the expected date, she asked me do a pregnancy test.( her compounder hurriedly put a pregnancy kit in my hand -(which she brought from pharmacy within a clinic). I even told her that my periods sometimes goes late by 2/3. * *** ********* ** ********* *** ** ******** **** ** **** **** * *** * ****** *** ******* * still i went ahead and did the test. They charged us 85 Rs. for the kit. ( Though Rs. 65 was written on the kit.) when asked,  20Rs. for the plastic bottle was the answerüòèlater when the test was negative, she did breast examination and suggested few medicines. but those medicines were not available with most of the chemists **** ***** ** **********The compounder said they are only sold in pharmacy of the clinic.which means we have to buy medicines from them only ** ****** ******
It was only my first visit and ma'am made sure to make me feel quite comfortable. Would definitely recommend her.
